@host = http://localhost:5123

### Tableau de bord
GET {{host}}/api/dashboard
Accept: application/json

### Liste des projets
GET {{host}}/api/projects
Accept: application/json

### Créer un projet
# @name createProject
POST {{host}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Migration SI",
  "description": "Refonte du SI interne",
  "owner": "A. Martin",
  "startDate": "2026-09-01",
  "deadline": "2026-12-15",
  "status": "InProgress"
}

### Détail d'un projet
@projectId = {{createProject.response.body.id}}
GET {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}
Accept: application/json

### Modifier le statut d'un projet
PATCH {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "Done" }

### Ajouter une tâche
POST {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cadrage technique",
  "description": "Analyse de l'existant",
  "priority": "High",
  "status": "InProgress"
}

### Tâches d'un projet
GET {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Accept: application/json

### Ajouter un livrable
POST {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/deliverables
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cahier des charges",
  "type": "Documentation",
  "pathOrUrl": "https://intranet/docs/cdc.pdf",
  "comment": "Version 1"
}

### Livrables d'un projet
GET {{host}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/deliverables
Accept: application/json
